  line `1 [ THE SCHEDULE`
  line `( See section 3 A )`
  line `( 1 ) Mines.`
  line `( 2 ) Inflammable substances or explosives.`
  line `( 3 ) Hazardous process.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this Schedule, “hazardous process” has the meaning assigned to it`
  line `in clause ( cb ) of the Factories Act, 1948 (63 of 1948) ].`
  line `1. Subs. b y Act 35 of 2016, s. 22, for the Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 9 - 2016).`
